# Repository policy: only project documentation and release zips are tracked.
# Everything else (source, build artifacts, configs, tests) stays local.

# Ignore everything by default
**

# Keep root-level project markdown files
!*.md

# Keep the one project doc inside tools/
!tools/
!tools/README.md

# Keep release zips in the root
!PalworldDiscordPlugin.zip
!PalworldDiscordPlugin_v*.zip

# Keep this gitignore file itself
!.gitignore
